### **4. 21_LiveTelemetryPlot**  
**Description:**  
A real-time plotting tool that displays incoming numeric data as a scrolling line chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveTelemetryPlot - Real-Time Chart Tool

LiveTelemetryPlot is great for streaming metrics, sensor values, and dashboard-style visual feedback.

## Features
- Scrollable real-time graph  
- Configurable refresh rate  
- Lightweight and responsive  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/21_LiveTelemetryPlot.git
cd 21_LiveTelemetryPlot
python visualize.py
